body.content:
I'm Alfred Norr Menesses from the United States but presently working
in Afghanistan. I have been trying to send an email to you for a
couple of days but each time I try sending, my message will return
back as a failure. Do not know where the fault was coming from. I have
not given up,still trying to send and interested to tell you my
purpose of contacting you. Kindly acknowledge receipt by return mail
if you eventually receive this. My photo is attached.

Your friend,
Sergeant A.N Menesses
